{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-describe-your-current-project/task-6","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-describe-your-current-project","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>James koristi <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Continuous</span> da govori o radnjama koje se dešavaju tokom govora ili u vezi s njim.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Continuous</span> sastoji se u sadašnjem vremenu glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to be</span> (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">am/is/are</span>), praćen je formom glavnog glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">-ing</span>. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I am using</span> u <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I am using special tools</span> pokazuje radnju koju James trenutno radi.</p>\n<p>Ovo vrijeme se često koristi za kratke ili tekuće radnje. Ostali primeri uključuju:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">She is studying for the interview.</span> - Trenutno se fokusira na čitanje.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">They are working on a new project.</span> - Oni su trenutno u projektu.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">He is walking to the station.</span> - On/Ona je u procesu hodanja ka stanici.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-describe-your-current-project/task-6"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Zašto Džejms koristi specijalni alat?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Da bi mu/njoj radio bio lakši.</p>","feedback":"<p>Iako alati olakšavaju rad, to nije glavni razlog zašto ih koristi.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Identifikujte potencijalne probleme.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Za